import Vue from 'vue'
import App from './App.vue'
import vuetify from './plugins/vuetify'
import router from './router/index'
import Vuex from 'vuex'
//import router from './router/index' //导入刚刚在route文件下定义的router

Vue.config.productionTip = false
Vue.use(router)
Vue.use(Vuex);

new Vue({
  vuetify,
  router, // 引入路由
  render: h => h(App)
}).$mount('#app')
